<plot>A Brokedown Melody explores the times, travels and experiences of a tribe of surfers who search for the spark of life and look to pass it on to the younger generation. The film follows swell through South America, Polynesia and Jamaica documenting the surfing and times of Kelly Slater, Jack Johnson, Gerry Lopez, Rob Machado and the Malloys. The title track is written &amp; performed by Jack Johnson, who also showcases his surfing skills.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?007935</url></doc>
